---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About the Math Club"
	description="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet"
	pubDate={new Date('Sept 10, 2024')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-1.jpg"
>	
	<h3>
		Mission
	</h3>

	<p>
		Our core mission is to propagate the passion for mathematics to everyone at Peddie. Regardless of their
		mathematical prowess, everyone can participate and engage in establishing an inclusive community of
		thinkers. We will create a comfortable space for avid mathematicians to express their passion that
		will emanate to other students at Peddie. We will offer opportunities to Peddie Students in a broader
		scope not restricted to the classroom and the traditional math curriculum, paving the way to develop
		intellectual talents capable of altering the globe.
	</p>
	<p>
		If you want to learn more about the organization of our club, click <a href="/constitution">here</a> to read our constitution.
	</p>

	<h3>
		Meet our Team
	</h3>

	<!-- Team Introduction Section -->
	<div class="team-container">
		<div class="team-member">
			<img src="/blog-placeholder-1.jpg" alt="Person 1">
			<h4>Jerry Liu</h4>
			<p>President of the Math Club</p>
			<p><a href="/bio1">Bio</a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="team-member">
			<img src="/blog-placeholder-2.jpg" alt="Person 2">
			<h4>Mark Zhao</h4>
			<p>Vice President of the Math Club</p>
			<p><a href="/bio2">Bio</a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="team-member">
			<img src="/blog-placeholder-3.jpg" alt="Person 3">
			<h4>Jayden Li</h4>
			<p>Secretary of the Math Club</p>
			<p><a href="/bio3">Bio</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- CSS for styling -->
	<style>
		.team-container {
			display: flex; /* Use Flexbox to create side-by-side layout */
			justify-content: space-around; /* Space out items evenly */
			flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow items to wrap if needed */
			margin-top: 20px;
		}

		.team-member {
			width: 200px; /* Set a fixed width for each member */
			text-align: center; /* Center-align text */
			margin: 5px;
		}

		.team-member img {
			width: 100%; /* Make image width 100% of the container */
			/* border-radius: 50%;*/ /* Make the image circular */
			margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add some space below the image */
		}

		.team-member h3 {
			margin: 2px 0; /* Adjust margin for the name */
		}

		.team-member p {
			color: #555; /* Set a slightly muted color for the text */
		}

		/* Media query to ensure images wrap around on mobile */
		@media (max-width: 600px) {
			.team-container {
				flex-direction: column; /* Stack items vertically */
				align-items: center; /* Center-align items */
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
